STATE of Louisiana
v.
Leonard COLLINS NO. 2018-KH-0800 Supreme Court of Louisiana. March 25, 2019

Denied. Applicant has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. See State ex rel. Collins v. State, 15-1876 (La. 12/16/16), 207 So.3d 1047.
